16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
18 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 158 of Title 17, unless there is
19 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
20 A. As used in this act:
21 1. “Advanced nuclear reactors” means nuclear reactors,
22 including small modular reactors or any necessary ancillary
23 facilities or structures, that are authorized by the United States
24
